===============SERIES INFO=============

Six players will play over the next 5 months to crown one winner!  We keep track of wins and losses which populate an ever changing leaderboard leading to a single elimination tournament at the end. Lets see which player comes out on top!

One twist this season is that while a player is allowed to play any faction they want, they can never play the same detachment twice!  Time to test your skill no matter what.  Lets see who wins the fabled Sword of Chadocles!

Mubin brings the Chaos knights to stomp the baby knights in the form of the Black Templar.  Will
